name: Misfits
description:
Choose your character!
1. Kato - half kappa half beastmen a lone warrior searching for his real parents, his love for noodles makes his quest turn to naught

2. Demeter, a knight from the kingdom of spade turn into a self proclaimed tree hugger- she seeks the legendary tree of ygg to hugs

3. Pamopam, a juggler that seeks his lost twins Pamipam - have anger issues, but quite loveable when you get to know him better
